    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Iustitia pariter ac <lb n="2"/>pietate caelestibus ad<lb break="no" n="3"/>que Romanae felicitatis <lb n="4"/>perpetuis <expan><abbr>fundatorib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d<am>d</am></abbr><ex>ominis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>ostris</ex></expan> Valentiniano et Valen<lb break="no" n="6"/>ti victoriosissimis prin<lb break="no" n="7"/>cipibus ac totius orbis <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustis</ex></expan> Antonius Dracon<lb break="no" n="9"/>tius <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ir</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>ag</abbr><ex>ens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>vic</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectorum</ex></expan> praeto<lb break="no" n="10"/>rio per Africanas provin<lb break="no" n="11"/>cias numini et maiestati<lb break="no" n="12"/>eorum semper dicatissi<lb break="no" n="13"/>mus
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The inscription is carved over one or probably two erased earlier texts.</p>
            </div>
